profile: Plumber Tacoma is a full service plumbing company serving all of Tacoma, WA and the surrounding communities, including Puyallup, Lakewood, Gig Harbor, and Bonney Lake. Our plumbers provide every type of residential and commercial plumbing service, specializing in leak and faucet repair, water heater and dishwasher installs, and new plumbing installations. Call us anytime, 24/7, for five-star customer service.
